PF-I-wilt   flower.ABS CORE.sg
`The flower wilted'

# correct word order with transitive verb: tr CoreNP CoreNP
Source: a:32
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {word order}
Nakita   ti      babai ti      lalaki
na-kita  ti      babai ti      lalaki
PF.T-saw CORE.sg girl  CORE.sg boy
`The girl saw the boy'

# incorrect word order with transitive verb: CoreNP tr CoreNP
Source: a:32
Vetted: s
Judgment: u
Phenomena: {word order}
Ti      babai nakita   ti      lalaki
ti      babai na-kita  ti      lalaki
